  "summary": {
    "en": "A 72-piece DIY fortress kit with glow-style play value for small indoor forts, towers, and tent frames.",
    "zh": "72件DIY堡垒拼搭套装，带有夜光玩法价值，适合小型室内堡垒、高塔和帐篷框架。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 72-piece configuration is easy to start with and suitable for younger builders learning basic frame construction.",
      "PP rods and connector balls support repeated assembly in homes, classrooms, and activity spaces.",
      "The kit can build triangular houses, towers, and compact play tents while encouraging spatial awareness.",
      "Glow-style positioning makes the product suitable for reading corners, night play, and gift retail."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "72件配置上手简单，适合低龄儿童学习基础框架搭建。",
      "PP杆件和连接球支持家庭、课堂和活动空间中的反复拆装。",
      "套装可搭建三角房屋、高塔和小型游戏帐篷，帮助培养空间认知。",
      "夜光主题定位适合阅读角、夜间玩法和礼品零售。"
    ]
  },
